at line 421: `await page.waitForLoadState('networkidle', { timeout: 10_000 }).catch(() => {});` - this waits only 10s for networkidle. On a slow UAT environment, Builder.io might take 20-30s to respond. Let me increase this to 30s.\n\nAlso, for the scroll loop, change 8 retries × 800ms = 6.4s to maybe 15 retries × 1000ms = 15s.\n\nLet me make these targeted fixes now.\n"}}
